                                                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Etats de sections postérieurs à 1822"@fr ,
                                                                                                                       "Initial register created after 1822"@en .


###  https://w3id.org/tabulae/id/codes/sourceType/EtatsDeSections_Av_1822
<https://w3id.org/tabulae/id/codes/sourceType/EtatsDeSections_Av_1822> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                                                <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> ,
                                                                                :SourceType ;
